column3: sallymforInsomniacs Vent Hole with James Corden
column5: SPOILER WARNING: A late night gathering for non serious palaver that does not speak of that night’s show. Posting a spoiler will get you brollywhacked. You don’t want that to happen to you.  This Vent Hole (hereafter known as IVH) if lost or stolen will not be replaced nor will the purchase price be refunded. Violation of IVH Rules will result in expulsion without a refund. A copy of IVH Rules can be obtained from one or more members wearing tie dyed oxford shirts after submitting a written request. Admission to certain functions within the IVH may require additional innuendo so enter at your own risk. Frivolity and silliness are highly recommended for all riders. Flamewars are expressly forbidden. Please consult your counselor magistrate or religious functionary before usage.  Good Evening fellow venthooligans! Don’t know where the time went! Not m much going on here.  Who’s Talking To Who? Jimmy Kimmel: Guests include Justin Theroux Mike Lindell and Tom Jones. Stephen Colbert: Stephen is live following President Biden's primetime address to a joint session of congress. Senator Bernie Sanders appears; Julia Michaels performs. Jimmy Fallon: Guests include Brian Regan and musical guest Rupi Kaur. James Corden: Jason Schwartzman appears; Gabby Barrett performs. Seth Meyers: Guests include Elisabeth Moss Ari Melber and musical guest Moon vs. Sun. Some stuff:
